<h1>DRAFT - Registration Districts</h1>

 <p class="lead"> This page provides details about the GRO's use of Registration Districts and their collation by the GRO into Volumes. It explains how FreeBMD makes use of their relationship between these during a search to indicate possible anomalies in the search results. It also highlights some of the problems that you may encounter when searching by Registration District, including the inconsistent district names and the changes in these names over time.</p> 

